<c.bg_transparent>How can I help you?</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:06:40.125 --> 00:06:43.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have a visitor, an old friend.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:06:44.083 --> 00:06:44.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Davion.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:06:45.041 --> 00:06:49.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't need to announce him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I envy him a bit, life on the road.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:06:49.791 --> 00:06:52.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Asar] It's not the Dragon Knight,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Your Radiance.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:06:52.125 --> 00:06:54.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's complicated.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:06:54.625 --> 00:06:59.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>She surrendered at the city gates,
demanding to see you.</i></c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:01.458 --> 00:07:03.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Mirana] And they threw her</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the stockade?</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:03.583 --> 00:07:07.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She insisted on it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>She said it was "comfortable."</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:09.125 --> 00:07:12.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Princess.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Empress Mirana, Her Majesty.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:12.333 --> 00:07:14.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right, Asar.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:14.291 --> 00:07:16.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Luna?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Forgive me, Empress.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:17.666 --> 00:07:20.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've come to swear my allegiance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Solar Goddess.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:20.875 --> 00:07:22.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've come to serve you.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:26.250 --> 00:07:29.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Luna] By the time we reached</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the first enclave, we started to see them.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:07:29.291 --> 00:07:31.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our own soldiers,</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:07:31.250 --> 00:07:34.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>wandering without the power Selemene</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>once granted.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:07:34.875 --> 00:07:38.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>To the men and women,
they told the same story,</i></c.bg_transparent>

123
00:07:38.250 --> 00:07:40.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>how the shrines came to life.</i></c.bg_transparent>

124
00:07:40.541 --> 00:07:43.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>How the goddess's blessing
coursed through them.</i></c.bg_transparent>

125
00:07:43.333 --> 00:07:47.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How they took their revenge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and gave the lie to a false prophecy.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:50.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yet some had questions.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:07:50.208 --> 00:07:52.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They wrestled with an emptiness</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in their guts,</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:07:52.833 --> 00:07:56.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they knew what love</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there may have been had passed.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:07:57.375 --> 00:08:02.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I gathered and sheltered them,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sent scouts far and wide to find more,</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:02.125 --> 00:08:04.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the lost, the broken, the undone.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:04.958 --> 00:08:07.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And you brought them all here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I brought them to you.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:07.958 --> 00:08:13.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You asked me to save them, and so I have,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and now I ask you to give them a purpose.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:13.250 --> 00:08:15.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give me a purpose.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:15.500 --> 00:08:19.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let us fight for you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Let us remake the world in your image.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:19.583 --> 00:08:22.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[chuckles lightly]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Remake the world?</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:22.291 --> 00:08:24.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can barely rebuild this place.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:24.750 --> 00:08:26.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because you think you're alone.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:26.500 --> 00:08:29.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We used to believe in something, we two.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:29.291 --> 00:08:32.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing is so broken it cannot be fixed.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:08:32.125 --> 00:08:34.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now you have the power to fix it all.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:08:34.666 --> 00:08:36.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The power of a god.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:08:36.333 --> 00:08:40.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The power of an empire. Most important…</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:08:40.375 --> 00:08:42.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>now you have me.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:08:43.916 --> 00:08:45.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[sentimental music]</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:08:46.041 --> 00:08:47.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Free her, Asar.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:08:48.291 --> 00:08:50.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Majesty! She is the Scourge.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:53.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She is my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:08:57.875 --> 00:08:58.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Jarl groans]</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:01.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Itches like the Fifth Hell.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:01.166 --> 00:09:04.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pretty sure these accouterments</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>don't come in Oglodi size.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:04.583 --> 00:09:08.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm certain those shiny sons</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of bitches would rather they never do.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:08.375 --> 00:09:11.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of it this way,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no one is staring at your ears.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:11.375 --> 00:09:13.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anyone says a word about your ears</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>answers to me.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:09:14.291 --> 00:09:16.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[sighs]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Now, fall in.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:09:16.208 --> 00:09:17.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Hieronimo clears throat]</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:09:18.625 --> 00:09:21.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If nothing fit,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you could at least wear a banner.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:21.333 --> 00:09:24.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no, no.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It is not that, my lovely. It is more.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:09:24.750 --> 00:09:31.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am still Nivan Gallant in my heart,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but, uh, my sword remains at your service.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:09:31.791 --> 00:09:33.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never cease to confuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:09:33.625 --> 00:09:35.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eh, we must all have goals.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:09:35.958 --> 00:09:41.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are certain this is yours,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this uniform, this banner?</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:09:41.708 --> 00:09:43.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not the banner, her.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:09:44.250 --> 00:09:47.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who kneels before the Solar Throne?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:09:47.333 --> 00:09:49.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Luna] I do, Your Radiance.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:09:49.458 --> 00:09:52.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Luna of the plains</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the Nightsilver Woods.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:09:52.625 --> 00:09:56.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I offer you my heart,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my courage, my steel.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:09:56.750 --> 00:09:59.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I seek your light, your love.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:09:59.500 --> 00:10:04.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take you as God Empress,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>first in thought, first in action.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:04.375 --> 00:10:07.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand in the light. And these soldiers?</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:08.041 --> 00:10:11.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Luna] My Lost Legion.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Many have fought for you already.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:11.541 --> 00:10:15.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their devotion is inscribed in scars,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>inked by pain.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:16.458 --> 00:10:20.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Accept the blessing of the Solar Throne,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Luna of the Imperium.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:22.291 --> 00:10:25.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Luna, the goddess of the Lost Legion.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:26.208 --> 00:10:28.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[hopeful music]</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:32.041 --> 00:10:34.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Together we will rebuild our home.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:35.708 --> 00:10:39.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then we will heal a broken world.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:46.916 --> 00:10:47.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Davion] Your Majesty.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:49.625 --> 00:10:50.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Mirana] Dragon Knight.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:10:53.041 --> 00:10:56.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you're home. Finally.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:10:58.833 --> 00:11:00.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[unsettling music]</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:01.666 --> 00:11:04.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Something's wrong.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Is Bram with you? Is he--</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:04.083 --> 00:11:05.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bram is fine. Bram is here.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:09.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Kaden, too.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then what?</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:10.208 --> 00:11:13.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Slyrak is dead. Slyrak failed.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:15.250 --> 00:11:17.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[dragons screeching]</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:21.666 --> 00:11:24.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[growling]</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:27.458 --> 00:11:29.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[screeching]</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:34.500 --> 00:11:37.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Invoker] I see you've abandoned subtlety.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:39.666 --> 00:11:43.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Drysi/Terrorblade]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The Father of Fire failed. You are alone.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:43.083 --> 00:11:47.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You betrayed or abandoned anyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who might have come to your aid,</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:47.375 --> 00:11:49.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the godling, the elves.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:50.166 --> 00:11:51.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Drysi/Terrorblade chuckle]</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:51.875 --> 00:11:54.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Drysi/Terrorblade]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I am all you have left in the world.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:54.583 --> 00:11:56.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Surrender the dragon souls,</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:56.625 --> 00:12:02.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and when I remake reality,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I will leave you a gift, your child,</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:02.500 --> 00:12:08.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>safe with you here,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>untouched in this oasis you've created.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:08.791 --> 00:12:12.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Immortal Filomena.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:12.166 --> 00:12:16.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is my bond, my renegotiation.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:16.166 --> 00:12:20.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You offer all revised terms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>per the original Shopkeeper's coven?</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:20.208 --> 00:12:23.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-[Drysi/Terrorblade] Inviolable.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-[Invoker] You guarantee…</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:23.125 --> 00:12:26.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the child will be my Filomena,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as I remember her.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:26.291 --> 00:12:27.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She'll be mine in every way.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:30.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Drysi/Terrorblade]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Filomena will love you in the next life</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:30.958 --> 00:12:32.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>as she loved you in this one.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:12:33.458 --> 00:12:36.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She'll be healthy,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>free of the rot that claimed her?</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:36.958 --> 00:12:41.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Drysi/Terrorblade]</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I promise, an eternity of flowers.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:41.208 --> 00:12:44.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What would you not do to feel her hand…</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:12:45.541 --> 00:12:47.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>in your own again?</i></c.bg_transparent>

209
00:12:48.916 --> 00:12:51.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
